%h3 Formatting Help
%p 
  You can use 
  = link_to "textile", "http://www.textism.com/tools/textile/", :target => '_blank'
  formatting if you wish. Here are a few of the most common features:
%p
  %table
    %tr
      %td To make text bold:
      %td
        %strong *bold*
    %tr
      %td To emphasize text:
      %td
        %em _emphasis_
    %tr
      %td To insert a link:
      %td
        %strong "linktext":url
    %tr
      %td Bulleted lists:
      %td
        %strong *
    %tr
      %td Numbered list:
      %td
        %strong #